data.description: Your search is over!! Welcome to this gorgeous and well-maintained single-family home nestled in beautiful Oak Lawn that that provides an abundance of ambiance, privacy, and relaxation.  This split-level gem has natural light illuminating the home giving a sense of warmth and comfort throughout.  This spacious and well-appointed home offers 3 bedrooms with large closets and 1.5 baths and hard wood floors throughout.  Nicely sized kitchen with stainless appliances that opens to a very spacious dining room.  Embrace the indoor-outdoor living as you step out onto the large 50 x 25 patio and have plenty of space with an oversized back yard ideal for entertaining and the family to enjoy.  Located in the prestigious Kolmar school district with Brother Rice, Marist, and St. Xavier just a 5-minute drive away.  Just a 30-minute train ride downtown with Metra as well as 5 minutes from shopping centers, hospitals, parks, pools, and numerous dining and entertainment options.  Embrace the beauty of natural surroundings and an inviting ambiance.  2012 - furnace, AC, kitchen remodel, appliances, concrete patio. 2014 - plumbing. 2019 - water heater, energy efficient (Wi-Fi) washer and dryer. 2020 - new (Wi-Fi) garage door. Seller currently with contract for interior to be professionally painted.  This one won't last long so come take a look!!
